					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b50e37f" data-id="b50e37f" data-element_type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
								<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-01c04d3 elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-wgl-toggle-accordion" data-id="01c04d3" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="wgl-toggle-accordion.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<div class="wgl-accordion icon-plus" id="wgl-accordion-01c04d3" data-type="toggle"><div class="accordion__panel"><h4 id="accordion__header-1831" class="accordion__header" data-default=""><span class="accordion__title">Can I acquire the IPTV service if I am not eligible for satellite service?</span><i class="accordion__icon elementor-icon "></i></h4><div class="accordion__content"><p><span>As IPTV brings global programming to your TV through the internet, the need for a satellite dish is eliminated. Additionally, to be eligible, a high-speed internet connection of at least 15.0 Mbps or higher is required.</span></p></div></div><div class="accordion__panel"><h4 id="accordion__header-1832" class="accordion__header" data-default=""><span class="accordion__title">Is there a refund policy in place?</span><i class="accordion__icon elementor-icon "></i></h4><div class="accordion__content"><p><span>We provide a 7-day money-back guarantee. If you are dissatisfied with the service, you can request a refund at any time, and we will process it within seven days.</span></p></div></div><div class="accordion__panel"><h4 id="accordion__header-1833" class="accordion__header" data-default=""><span class="accordion__title">Is there an Electronic Program Guide (EPG) included in your IPTV service?</span><i class="accordion__icon elementor-icon "></i></h4><div class="accordion__content"><p><span>Certainly, EPG (Electronic Program Guide) coverage is available for 80% of our channels. If you experience any challenges with the EPG, feel free to reach out to us for assistance.</span></p></div></div><div class="accordion__panel"><h4 id="accordion__header-1834" class="accordion__header" data-default=""><span class="accordion__title">What is the bandwidth consumption of the IPTV stream?</span><i class="accordion__icon elementor-icon "></i></h4><div class="accordion__content"><p><span>Employing cutting-edge H.264 technology, our services ensure optimal compression and top-notch quality. The IPTV stream sizes typically hover around 8 Mbit. It's worth noting that when switching channels, the H.264 protocol may experience a temporary spike before displaying the picture. This underscores the importance of having a minimum internet connection speed of 16 Mbit, rising to 30 Mbit for HD channels.</span></p></div></div><div class="accordion__panel"><h4 id="accordion__header-1835" class="accordion__header" data-default=""><span class="accordion__title">What should I do if my channel is experiencing freezing issues?</span><i class="accordion__icon elementor-icon "></i></h4><div class="accordion__content"><p><span>If you encounter a pause while watching a channel, try selecting and opening another channel. Then, return to the original channel to check if it is now playing. This pause may occur due to a brief interruption in transmission, causing the software to temporarily halt.</span></p></div></div><div class="accordion__panel"><h4 id="accordion__header-1836" class="accordion__header" data-default=""><span class="accordion__title">
What steps should I take if my account is not functioning properly?</span><i class="accordion__icon elementor-icon "></i></h4><div class="accordion__content"><p>Initially, please verify your network connection, restart both your router and device, and attempt to reconnect.</p><p>Subsequently, if your network connection remains stable, assess whether your account is concurrently in use on other devices, as it allows simultaneous viewing on multiple devices.</p></div></div></div>		</div>
				</div>
